WEBVTT

00:03:28.567 --> 00:03:32.346
and then I learned
one in five American women

00:03:32.370 --> 00:03:34.687
won't be having a biological child --

00:03:34.711 --> 00:03:37.544
some by choice, some by chance.

00:03:37.568 --> 00:03:38.757
(Applause)

00:03:38.781 --> 00:03:41.144
But I was not alone.

00:03:43.192 --> 00:03:45.907
But the more I read,
the more disheartened I became.

00:03:45.931 --> 00:03:48.738
I read women's stories,

00:03:48.762 --> 00:03:51.476
trying desperately to get this procedure.

00:03:52.534 --> 00:03:58.929
I learned how common it was
for women to exhaust their finances

00:03:58.953 --> 00:04:04.429
appealing to dozens of ob-gyns
over many years,